abstract: >-
  A research-grade privacy policy analysis tool specifically designed for
  healthcare applications. Combines advanced Large Language Model (LLM)
  analysis, statistical methods, and comprehensive validation to provide
  publication-quality insights into privacy policies. Features multi-model
  support (Claude Sonnet 4, GPT-4), three analysis depths including
  chain-of-thought reasoning, comparative statistical analysis, anomaly
  detection, and complete research workflow automation. Includes quality
  validation, intelligent caching, and production-ready Docker deployment.
  Designed for academic research in healthcare privacy, HIPAA compliance,
  and digital health policy analysis.

